abstract: NHL Roundup; Florida Panthers defeat New York Islanders, 3-2; other hockey scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Aleksander Barkov scored the winner in a five-round shootout on Friday night, and the Florida Panthers beat the visiting Islanders, 3-2.

headline.main: Isles Miss Once in 5-Round Shootout, and Lose
